1032
01:35:23,746 --> 01:35:26,112
你和洛琳正巧路过真是太好了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}lt's a good thing you and Lureen happened along when you did...{\r}

1033
01:35:26,181 --> 01:35:28,308
要不我们只能困在路上
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}or else we'd still be stuck on the side of the road...{\r}

1034
01:35:28,384 --> 01:35:29,646
那破旧货车里
