1053
01:36:24,106 --> 01:36:26,199
为罗伊 泰勒工作，你会满意的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You'll like working for Roy Taylor.{\r}

1054
01:36:26,275 --> 01:36:29,472
