1058
01:36:48,263 --> 01:36:50,891
那天抽个周末我们去玩玩
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We ought to go down there some weekend.{\r}

1059
01:36:51,734 --> 01:36:54,168
喝喝酒，钓钓鱼
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Drink a little whiskey, fish some.{\r}

1060
01:36:55,571 --> 01:36:57,835
放松一下
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get away, you know?{\r}

1061
01:37:01,043 --> 01:37:02,533
就在离开南卫理公会大学之后
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}(LaShawn) That was right out of SMU.{\r}

1062
01:37:02,611 --> 01:37:05,079
