{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}So my pick was Neiman Marcus, which was a disaster...{\r}

1064
01:37:07,583 --> 01:37:10,677
因为，亲爱的，只要是和衣服相关的 我就无法抗拒了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}because, honey, where clothes is concerned, l got no resistance.{\r}

1065
01:37:10,753 --> 01:37:14,018
我真的入不敷出 连兰德尔的薪水也不够
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}l was spending more than l made. More than Randall ever will make.{\r}

1066
01:37:14,089 --> 01:37:15,078
我们来到这
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We come out here...{\r}

1067
01:37:15,157 --> 01:37:17,250
以为经营牧场还是 大盖帽和万宝路之类的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}thinkin' that ranchin' was still big hats and Marlboros.{\r}

1068
01:37:17,326 --> 01:37:19,260
天啊，我们可是落伍了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Boy, were we behind the times.{\r}

1069
01:37:35,878 --> 01:37:38,073
嗨，乖女，准备好了？
