1076
01:38:09,278 --> 01:38:11,906
还是你觉得我不适合他？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Or you don't think l'm the one for him?{\r}

1077
01:38:12,014 --> 01:38:13,845
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}[people chattering]{\r}


1078
01:38:14,683 --> 01:38:16,412
