{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You're good enough.{\r}

1079
01:38:16,485 --> 01:38:19,318
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}@@{MeIissa by The Allman Brothers playing]{\r}


1080
01:38:21,490 --> 01:38:24,687
