1083
01:38:32,100 --> 01:38:33,192
好了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}All right.{\r}

1084
01:38:34,036 --> 01:38:36,561
还不能让你闲着，牛仔
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You're stayin' on your feet, cowboy.{\r}

1085
01:38:37,673 --> 01:38:39,163
失陪，亲爱的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Excuse me, darling.{\r}

1086
01:39:02,064 --> 01:39:05,727
下周礼拜过后 我来接你和珍妮
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}So l'll pick you and Jenny up next weekend, after church.{\r}

1087
01:39:07,202 --> 01:39:08,294
好
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Fine.{\r}

1088
01:39:11,974 --> 01:39:13,464
你没事吧？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You all right?{\r}

1089
01:39:14,776 --> 01:39:15,834
没
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes.{\r}

1090
01:39:17,045 --> 01:39:18,512
真的？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Are you sure?{\r}

1091
01:39:21,783 --> 01:39:24,946
爸爸，我在想 又生了孩子后…
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Daddy, l was thinking, what with the new baby and all...{\r}

1092
01:39:25,020 --> 01:39:27,420
