{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Ma and Monroe have been awful strict on me.{\r}

1093
01:39:27,489 --> 01:39:29,582
比对珍妮还要严
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}More on me than Jenny even.{\r}

1094
01:39:30,492 --> 01:39:32,824
我想，或许我…
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}l was thinkin', maybe l could....{\r}

1095
01:39:34,997 --> 01:39:37,397
或许我可以搬来和你一起住
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Maybe l could come stay with you.{\r}

1096
01:39:38,567 --> 01:39:41,400
我能帮你大忙的，我肯定
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}l'd be an awful good help, l know l would.{\r}

1097
01:39:41,837 --> 01:39:44,829
