{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Now, you know l ain't set up for that.{\r}

1098
01:39:46,675 --> 01:39:48,802
马上就要赶牧了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}With the roundup comin'...{\r}

1099
01:39:49,478 --> 01:39:51,275
