1101
01:39:54,917 --> 01:39:58,876
- 我不是说我不想… - 没关系，我懂
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}l'm not sayin' that l wouldn't-- lt's all right, l understand.{\r}

1102
01:40:01,256 --> 01:40:03,486
