{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, see you on Sunday, then.{\r}

1103
01:40:04,459 --> 01:40:05,517
再见
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Bye.{\r}

1104
01:40:08,063 --> 01:40:09,655
再见，亲爱的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Bye, sweetheart.{\r}

1105
01:40:39,194 --> 01:40:41,492
今晚肯定下雪
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Going to snow tonight for sure.{\r}

1106
01:40:42,731 --> 01:40:43,789
对
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Yup.{\r}

1107
01:40:51,440 --> 01:40:54,898
