1112
01:41:14,296 --> 01:41:16,321
你和洛琳呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What about you and Lureen?{\r}

1113
01:41:18,834 --> 01:41:21,632
在生意上再怎样也难不倒洛琳
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Lureen's good at making hard deals in the machinery business...{\r}

1114
01:41:21,703 --> 01:41:24,137
可至于我们的婚姻
